rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0002
rows.name: Oh, so you finally dragged yourselves back, eh?

rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0003
rows.name:
Coming all the way out here to meet us?
We were heading to HQ anyway.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0004
rows.name: Just couldn't wait any longer, eh?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0005
rows.name: It's faster if I come here and ask, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs02050100_MSG0006
rows.name:
It seems you took some time, but
well, for a first time, it's well done.[ST:wait ]
